{"type": "article", "id": 29509, "title": "模块式衣帽架", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-12T23:01:52Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160712222225zeYpTXoPgtDSK4k3.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>再平凡无奇的日用品都能启发有趣又实用的创意：纽约 <a href=\"http://www.hcwangdesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">HCWD Studio</a> 的两位设计师 Sin-Chun Wang 和 Ye Liu 就以生活中常见的晾衣竿为灵感，打造一款名为 <a href=\"http://www.hcwangdesign.com/blog/?p=548\" rel=\"nofollow\">Y-rack</a> 的衣帽架。由于采用了模块化设计，用户可以根据需要自由定制衣帽架的造型，使用起来非常灵活。如果你对 Y-rack 感兴趣的话，可以参加它在 Kickstarter 上计划于 7 月 26 日开始的众筹活动。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712222244Z7qylSmiX0Wsj9aD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712222244XdJA5fU1L0W3zjqO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607122222440kQSJbIagoVELjCp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712222245cqhCAS1M4ompYJzQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}